[MATH text=R\_I=\frac{U\_c}{I\_R}=\frac{R\_cI\_c}{I-I\_c}=\frac{360\ Ω\cdot0{,}10\ mA}{\left(100-0{,}10\right)\ mA}=0{,}36036036...Ω\approx0{,}36\ Ω]

